      <p>
        In designing the questionnaire,we took into account a
number of references[3, 4, 8, 121 regarding risk management,
and such manuals on analyzing risky projects as are
currently used at Company A. We then summarized the factors
defining risky projects and classified them according to the
following five areas: (1) Requirements, (
